<abstract><t>This document describes procedures on providing optimal routing for IPv4 Internet traffic based on the shortest IGP metric.  It builds on the ability of advertising multiple paths for a given destination prefix, using BGP Add-Path and provides a solution for selectively indicating preferences towards BGP path(s) via affinities.</t></abstract>

